snippet.title: Road Guy Rob
snippet.description:
We use transportation every day.  Let's stop and explore how it works! 



[Copyright info:]  Yes, please DO show my videos in any useful setting (educational, civic, business, etc).  Consider tweeting me @roadguyrob when you do.  No requirement; I'd just love to hear about it.
